messages.messageBody:
Hi Nicki,

I saw your intro and had a question about your sewing for the EC store. What do you mean?...just a question from a mom who is starting to look for a work at home opportunity.

And, I'm from Minnesoa...grew up in west central Minnesota, not far from Fargo-Moorhead. And then as a new parent, I lived near St. Cloud. I'm in Virginia now...with mostly all of my relatives still residing back home. What area are you in?

Katy
